<br />

<br />
If the pets are appropriately tuned in DPS, I don't care that the nukes "seem low" in output. The bottom line is that pet DPS has not scaled with overall DPS in the game and are still "trapped" at early PoP levels. 
<br />

<br />
The higher-level <span style="font-style: italic">(edit) <span style="font-weight: bold">pet </span></span>focus pieces don't do diddly for scaling mage power either. I am disappointed that this is not addressed, but it appears that this is a "popularity" contest for getting attention.
<br />

